approach :

Seach Node temp

cases :

temp has 0 child
    just delete and return null


temp has 1 child 
    store its left or right whichever is available delete temp and return stored Node 

temp has 2 child
    
    merge with left 
    go find max value is the left subtree and replace temp data with maxVal then delete maxVal Node 

    merge with right 
    go find min value is the right subtree and replace temp data with minVal then delete minVal Node 


minVal - go on the leftmost of root;
maxVal - go no the rightmost of root